snippet.textDisplay:
Three seasons have gone by and #CokeStudio under Strings is sounding more of a punjabi studio with other regions and their rich music being ignored ! What surprises most is that although being recorded and produced in Karachi (Sindh) , we havent witnessed any sindhi song as Strings have taken over. This is where I loved the Rohail era perhaps , he brought the most indigineous sounds of Tahir Mithu , Sketches and Faqeer Zulfiqar to limelight ! <3 ! His perein puwandee san still gives me ghoosebumps ! 
Sorry to say but by ignoring rich traditional music of other regions , Coke Studio can be said a commercialized attempt rather than staying to true essence of music revival for which it was made (Y) !
